                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, wie daz ir in etwievil weins czu Sluszelfeld
                        genomen und hinweg gefürt habt. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir
                                <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> iren weine
                            <expan>widergeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und on hindernüsse volgen lassen
                        wöllet <add><expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan></add>, als etc. Das
                                <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. Und lat uns des
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>freuntl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> wissen bey disem
                        <expan>bote<ex>n</ex></expan>.</ab>
